      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――遊園地ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これは、ちょっと困ったな……",
      "startTime": 2.6666665793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "困りましたね……",
      "startTime": 5.833333246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ある程度予想していたことだが……",
      "startTime": 8.6077777466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地に来てるお客さんがとても少ないです……",
      "startTime": 11.7255554438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "来場者が減っているというのは本当のようだな\nライブが始まるまでに人が集まるといいが",
      "startTime": 20.727186243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "頑張って遊園地を盛り上げなきゃですね\nよーし、やりますよー！",
      "startTime": 27.866664815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、私が歌う特設ステージは\nどこにあるんですか？",
      "startTime": 35.5999981483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "向こうの広場に作られているはずだ\nあっ、あれじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 40.7692267183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あれは……思ってたより小さいステージですね\nとても素朴で、手作り感が凄いです",
      "startTime": 48.2333314817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、座席も段差もないです。後ろの人や\n背の低い人は、ステージがよく見えないかも……",
      "startTime": 56.7333314817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "地図を見ただけでは分からなかったが\nステージは広場の外から見え辛い場所にあるな",
      "startTime": 64.3894763712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "たまたま遊園地に遊びに来た人は\nここでライブをしていても気付かなそうだ",
      "startTime": 70.6894763712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "それは困ります！　遊園地を盛り上げるためにも\n出来るだけ沢山の人にライブを観てほしいです",
      "startTime": 77.7999981483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私のライブを観て、遊園地の楽しい思い出を\n作ってもらいたいです……",
      "startTime": 86.0333314817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われても、ステージをここから\n動かす訳にはいかないしな……",
      "startTime": 91.3527965025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ステージを動かす……？\nそれです！　ライブステージを動かしましょう！",
      "startTime": 98.7333314817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　楽しんでますかー！",
      "startTime": 104.686347795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "今日だけの特別企画！\nアイドルのスペシャルパレードが始まりますよ～！",
      "startTime": 112.16505095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "これから私、サニーピースの川咲さくらが\nライブをしながら園内をパレードしちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 120.5333274127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "歌とダンスで遊園地を盛り上げるから\nみんなもついて来てね！",
      "startTime": 127.8666582029,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1470.2318514000012,
          "startTime": 129.3368900543
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（凄いな、どんどん人が集まってくるぞ。パレードで）\n（ライブするというさくらのアイデアは大成功だ）",
      "startTime": 134.1553682413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "この乗り物、凄いと思いませんか？　これはもともと\nこの遊園地のパレードで使ってた物なんです",
      "startTime": 142.7333330076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "パレードをやらなくなった今も\nスタッフのみなさんがちゃんと手入れしてたんですよ",
      "startTime": 149.2666785479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらがパレードをやりたいと言い出した時）\n（スタッフさん達も進んで協力してくれた）",
      "startTime": 156.6512795216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（いつかパレードを復活させたいと思ってたから）\n（願いが叶ったと言ってくれて……）",
      "startTime": 162.884608786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "大人も子供も、みんなが笑顔になる遊園地が\n私は大好きです！",
      "startTime": 169.7333279213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "私と一緒に笑顔の思い出を作ろうね！\nさあ、遊園地を遊び尽くすよー！",
      "startTime": 176.0383964293,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3194.936904000002,
          "startTime": 179.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブを成功させたい……遊園地を盛り上げたい……）\n（さくらの強い想いが、みんなの心を一つにした結果だ）",
      "startTime": 184.679633785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（今日、遊園地を訪れた人達にとって）\n（さくらのパレードは忘れられない思い出になりそうだ）",
      "startTime": 192.4276276357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 197.6609538482,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1439.0460803000167,
          "startTime": 199.0999999285
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nおはようございます！",
      "startTime": 201.2666754961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、さくら\n遊園地からさくら宛に手紙が届いてるぞ",
      "startTime": 204.8357611902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
